Hello! We’re releasing two repos to the public this year.

Robot 2020
This is the latest code from our 2020-2021 robot, Krono-Z

Robot-Swerve-Test
A code snapshot from our swerve drivetrain test robot. Some of the code was ported to Python from the Java repo found here: Swerve Drive Specialties

Feel free to hit us with any questions.
